description.Name: description
description.Value: In honor of the Nab Cup 2013 and the new season ahead of Australian Football, we bring you a weapon. Australian Field Football was founded two years ago to raise awareness for carcinoid cancer while saluting Australian Football. We kick carcinoid cancer. Visit us online at fieldfootball.com our goalpost converts for Football & Rugby. We have team mode! Teams are four on four. View over 600 videos on our channel. We need warriors to join our battle here and abroad. Message us here to join the battle against the slow killer carcinoid cancer. This sport is for my Aunt. It shall serve as her phoenix, with love.
